    "body": "MoE refactor followed #31504. Wrap unquantized `rocm_aiter_fused_expert` into modular kernel format. \n\n## Testing\nTest `gsm8k` eval before and after the change\n\nLaunch command\n```\nVLLM_ROCM_USE_AITER=1 vllm serve Qwen/Qwen3-30B-A3B\n```\n\nBenchmark command\n```\n    lm_eval \\\n            --model local-completions \\\n            --tasks gsm8k \\\n            --model_args \"model=Qwen/Qwen3-30B-A3B,base_url=http://localhost:8000/v1/completions,num_concurrent=1000,tokenized_requests=False\"\n```\n\nBefore this PR:\n```\n|Tasks|Version|     Filter     |n-shot|  Metric   |   |Value |   |Stderr|\n|-----|------:|----------------|-----:|-----------|---|-----:|---|-----:|\n|gsm8k|      3|flexible-extract|     5|exact_match|↑  |0.8006|±  |0.0110|\n|     |       |strict-match    |     5|exact_match|↑  |0.8855|±  |0.0088|\n```\n\nAfter:\n```\n|Tasks|Version|     Filter     |n-shot|  Metric   |   |Value |   |Stderr|\n|-----|------:|----------------|-----:|-----------|---|-----:|---|-----:|\n|gsm8k|      3|flexible-extract|     5|exact_match|↑  |0.8105|±  |0.0108|\n|     |       |strict-match    |     5|exact_match|↑  |0.8969|±  |0.0084|\n```",
    "created_at": "2025-12-30T18:57:51Z",
    "updated_at": "2026-01-05T22:58:42Z",
